---
import FeatureList from '@/components/FeatureList.astro';
---

<section class="section s3-problem">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="s3-problem__heading">The Challenge of Maintaining Healthy, Radiant Skin</h2>

    <p class="s3-problem__body">Dealing with skin problems can be frustrating and confidence-draining.</p>

    <p class="s3-problem__body">Environmental factors and aging leave skin looking dull, uneven, and congested despite your best efforts.</p>

    <p class="s3-problem__body">When searching for a hydrafacial near me, you deserve a treatment that delivers real, lasting results.</p>

    <FeatureList
      items={[
        "Conventional products rarely penetrate deep enough to address the root causes of skin concerns",
        "Seasonal changes and stress constantly challenge skin's balance",
        "Different facial areas have completely different needs",
      ]}
    />

    <p class="s3-problem__body">Traditional facial treatments offer only temporary relief without addressing underlying skin health.</p>

    <p class="s3-problem__body">With diverse skin types, standard facials frequently disappoint and leave clients searching for something more effective.</p>

    <p class="s3-problem__body">Thankfully we found the answer.</p>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-problem__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-problem__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
